{"tid":498746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"研究：吸煙會降低你對異性的吸引力","createTime":"2017-12-14T05:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T12:36:44.000Z","uid":72478,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ad466846a5908f103269b07727b166bac7aaac13","tid":498746,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"英國布里斯托大學一項最新調研訮究指出：吸煙者對異性的訪日吸引力較低。受訪者當中有三分之二的男性表示，不吸煙的女性較有吸引力。68%的女性也表示：不吸煙的男性更有魅力。<br />\n<br />\n上述調查有500人受訪。他們對23對雙胞胎的男性或女性作出評價。這些孿生兄弟或姊妹當 中，其中一個是癮君子，另一個不是。 <br />\n<br />\n結果顯示：不吸煙的那個吸引更多異性注意。 負責調查的研究人員說，一般人認為吸煙的人影響了他們的皮膚，因此影響了他們的儀容。 上述研究於是利用雙胞胎的人來進行測驗。因為他們外表基本上是「一樣的」。<br />\n<br />\n研究結果顯示外表對異性的吸引力的確重要，尤其在年青人心目中。 吸煙會讓人加快衰老。煙草中的尼古丁會讓皮膚底下的血管外層膜收縮，因而破壞了皮膚的彈性。臉部皺紋 是因為吸煙時吸入的動作形成的。上述研究結論，未來或可說服更多的人戒煙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/health/article-5173503/Smokers-attractive-opposite-sex-study-finds.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fhealth%2Farticle-5173503%2FSmokers-attractive-opposite-sex-study-finds.html&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e5afa6b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/health/article-5173503/Smokers-attractive-opposite-sex-study-finds.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/135221_f979578dc69104a1c2b3b135e5a426f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F135221_f979578dc69104a1c2b3b135e5a426f4.jpg&h=73affc87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/135244_ae001f0093916f65e93165403c5eb19d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F135244_ae001f0093916f65e93165403c5eb19d.jpg&h=4d8a0ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/41/MK_gal_zzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F41%2FMK_gal_zzz.jpg&h=b29999da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e12beb5ba0527105fd105cf73538098f5174ec89","tid":498746,"uid":69083,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"講咁多研究廢話無用，總之<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煙剷死全家</span>"},{"pid":"c3179383393e72269b6b721bb1dc743394e4d1b5","tid":498746,"uid":19604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291462a5bc3847e50a8cd81e09191dccded68c7d","tid":498746,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國有咩問題"},{"pid":"d95925cd081183ecb8f7c1d88f298955a52a674f","tid":498746,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"肺癌仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43d9b87094a7084fa1d7777dd8e4a83af23a19d","tid":498746,"uid":18724,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/c5/78/65/c57865007240e971aa2f35d51cb1bbe1--leonardo-di-caprio-beautiful-people.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2Fc5%2F78%2F65%2Fc57865007240e971aa2f35d51cb1bbe1--leonardo-di-caprio-beautiful-people.jpg&h=8e4efe2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b90e554aa79c0c12a0d898946f36a3d5d595025","tid":498746,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"噴煙女張picture都有一定年資<br />\n<br />\n應該差不多殘花敗柳"},{"pid":"048ba77a4d878cd9f88352be12391ba23c797c48","tid":498746,"uid":18604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人<